ng to find a rare_gm_03 to be nice enough to return you to order.  It would give the majority of players on blue servers a chance to experience a whole other side of eq with their characters rather then forcing them to try and play on those pk servers where ppl can be asses.  Personally, I'd like to see more guilds using /guildwar option too.<br>
